<div id="comment_status_65483512" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_65483512" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_65483512" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65483512" name="comment_link_65483512" href="//linux.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23731066&amp;cid=65483512" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65483512)" >Re: nope, also rust people</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65483512" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65483512); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Fons_de_spons">Fons_de_spons</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Fons_de_spons">( 1311177 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
