			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65483534" name="comment_link_65483534" href="//linux.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23731066&amp;cid=65483534" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65483534)" >Re:How to Win Friends and Influence People</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65483534" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65483534); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
